<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background: #667eea; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎬 Welcome to ReelAfrika!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Welcome to <strong>ReelAfrika</strong> - Your home for authentic African storytelling!</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you join our community. Get ready to explore captivating movies, series, and documentaries that celebrate African culture and creativity.</p>
      <p>To get started, please verify your email address:</p>
      <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
      <p>Once verified, you'll unlock:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ Personalized recommendations</li>
        <li>✅ Unlimited streaming</li>
        <li>✅ Exclusive African content</li>
        <li>✅ Multi-device support</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Happy watching!</p>
      <p><strong>The ReelAfrika Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 ReelAfrika. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Nairobi, Kenya | <a href="mailto:support@reelafrika.com">support@reelafrika.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>